 ## Steps
 
 1. Create or locate the one-person `goodwork/` workspace. Ensure `.env` is gitignored, initialize missing v2 state files from [state.md](state.md), and record any legacy Markdown files that need migration.
diff --git a/skills/goodwork/reference/state.md b/skills/goodwork/reference/state.md
index bd6a3fa6c49b918cdfc5b55e22b3ce31a9604163..9b3d5ecec6bfd6f94b3774929aa8311fdc2a20f9
--- a/skills/goodwork/reference/state.md
